---
// About section - merges About + Benefits
---

<section id="about" class="bg-warm-white py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 md:gap-14 items-center">

      <!-- Left Column: Image -->
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Decorative blurred circles -->
          <div class="absolute -z-10 -top-8 -left-8 w-64 h-64 bg-sage-200/40 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
          <div class="absolute -z-10 -bottom-8 -right-8 w-48 h-48 bg-gold-light/30 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

          <img
            src="/nails-work.jpg"
            alt="Professionelle Fußpflege bei Ella Schön in Erligheim"
            class="aspect-[4/5] object-cover w-full border-4 border-gold-light shadow-xl"
            style="border-radius: 40% 60% 50% 50% / 55% 45% 55% 45%"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Content -->
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
        <span class="bg-sage-50 text-sage-dark uppercase tracking-wider text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full inline-block font-body">
          &Uuml;ber uns
        </span>

        <h2 class="font-display text-olive text-3xl md:text-4xl mt-4 mb-4">
          Willkommen bei
          <span class="text-sage">Unser Salon bei Ella Sch&ouml;n</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="font-body text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Mein Name ist Elena Schneider, und ich lade Sie herzlich in meinen Salon in Erligheim ein.
          Mit Leidenschaft und Sorgfalt widme ich mich der professionellen kosmetischen Fu&szlig;pflege,
          damit Sie sich rundum wohlf&uuml;hlen und Ihre F&uuml;&szlig;e in besten H&auml;nden wissen.
        </p>

        <p class="font-body text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Jede Behandlung wird individuell auf Ihre Bed&uuml;rfnisse abgestimmt. Mir liegt es am Herzen,
          Ihnen nicht nur gepflegte F&uuml;&szlig;e, sondern auch eine Auszeit vom Alltag zu schenken &ndash;
          in einer gem&uuml;tlichen und entspannten Atmosph&auml;re.
        </p>

        <!-- Credentials Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-8">

          <!-- 1. Mehrfach Zertifiziert -->
          <div class="bg-sage-50/50 hover:bg-sage-50 p-4 rounded-organic-sm transition-colors flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-sage-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sage" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6" />
                <path d="M15.477 12.89 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-body font-semibold text-olive text-sm">Mehrfach Zertifiziert</p>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">Professionelle Zertifizierungen in kosmetischer Fu&szlig;pflege</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 2. Professionell -->
          <div class="bg-sage-50/50 hover:bg-sage-50 p-4 rounded-organic-sm transition-colors flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-sage-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sage" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
                <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" />
                <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87" />
                <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-body font-semibold text-olive text-sm">Professionell</p>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">Qualifizierte Ausbildung und individuelle Betreuung</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 3. Mit Leidenschaft -->
          <div class="bg-sage-50/50 hover:bg-sage-50 p-4 rounded-organic-sm transition-colors flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-sage-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sage" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-body font-semibold text-olive text-sm">Mit Leidenschaft</p>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">Individuelle und einf&uuml;hlsame Betreuung</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 4. Höchste Hygiene -->
          <div class="bg-sage-50/50 hover:bg-sage-50 p-4 rounded-organic-sm transition-colors flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-sage-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sage" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10" />
                <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-body font-semibold text-olive text-sm">H&ouml;chste Hygiene</p>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">Sterilisierte Instrumente nach medizinischen Standards</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 5. Gemütliches Ambiente -->
          <div class="bg-sage-50/50 hover:bg-sage-50 p-4 rounded-organic-sm transition-colors flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-sage-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sage" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M15 21v-8a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v8" />
                <path d="M3 10a2 2 0 0 1 .709-1.528l7-5.999a2 2 0 0 1 2.582 0l7 5.999A2 2 0 0 1 21 10v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-body font-semibold text-olive text-sm">Gem&uuml;tliches Ambiente</p>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">Entspannen Sie in angenehmer Salon-Atmosph&auml;re</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 6. Flexible Termine -->
          <div class="bg-sage-50/50 hover:bg-sage-50 p-4 rounded-organic-sm transition-colors flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-sage-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sage" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2" ry="2" />
                <line x1="16" x2="16" y1="2" y2="6" />
                <line x1="8" x2="8" y1="2" y2="6" />
                <line x1="3" x2="21" y1="10" y2="10" />
                <path d="m9 16 2 2 4-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-body font-semibold text-olive text-sm">Flexible Termine</p>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">Terminvereinbarung nach Ihren W&uuml;nschen</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
